		</a>
		<h1 class="title">如何将一个大众口味的啤酒品牌做成百年老店</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/2007/small/2007.jpg?1408114682" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">许冰清 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-24 08:52:29 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
		<img src="/system/articles/longshows/9933/medium/9933.jpg?1432304459" alt="" />
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="9933" data-title="《如何将一个大众口味的啤酒品牌做成百年老店》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9933/medium/9933.JPG?1436653554" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9933.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
